Mall of the North in conjunction with Segopje Soccer Masters Players embarked on a project to purchase school shoes and socks for 46 learners of Sesoai Primary School in Segopje, Ga-Mamabolo. The mall also donated 60 gift bags with rulers, note books and T-shirts to learners of the school. Public Relations and Promotions Manager Tabitha Lekganyane, far left, and Marketing Manager Mari Delport, far right, hands over the donations to the learners. &nbsp;